type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"the-links"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Links"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://supergobo.itch.io/out-of-thyme","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Out of Thyme"}]},{"type":"text","value":" (play the game)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://itch.io/jam/mini-jame-gam-20/rate/2205815","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Submission page"}]},{"type":"text","value":" (see other jammers' comments on my game)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://itch.io/jam/mini-jame-gam-20/results","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Jam results"}]},{"type":"text","value":" (see the rankings)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"the-tools"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Tools"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Here are the tools I chose to develop with:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Godot 4 (game engine, coding)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Krita (art)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Audacity (sound editing)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Aseprite (when didn't know how to do something in Krita)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FL Studio (when I didn't know how to do something in Audacity)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"the-process"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Process"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I woke up around 7 on Friday and immediately checked the theme: "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"out of time"}]},{"type":"text","value":". In addition to the theme, a special item had to be incorporated: "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"organ (the instrument)"}]},{"type":"text","value":". I had no ideas, so the first step was brainstorming."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Within a couple hours, I was actively sketching out game concepts with several friends. There were several good ideas, but the ones i resonated with most were action arcade games."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img-row","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img","props":{"src":"/images/games/out-of-thyme/20230808092547.png","className":["invert-when-light"]},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Someone came up with the idea to use \"running out of "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"thyme"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\" as a pun. This directed my attention first to farming, and then to a \"thyme defender\" arcade game."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img-row","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img","props":{"src":"/images/games/out-of-thyme/Untitled-2023-07-07-1953.png","className":["invert-when-light"]},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The final concept I ran with was a thyme delivery game where you defend your thyme from hungry birds by playing an organ. The final game stayed very true to my sketches."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img-row","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img","props":{"src":"/images/games/out-of-thyme/Untitled-2023-07-07-1953(2).png","className":["invert-when-light"]},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The next order of business was art. One of my goals for this jam was to make a game "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"without pixel art"}]},{"type":"text","value":", since that would stretch me out of my comfort zone."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I started by drawing a mockup of what I thought a screenshot of the game might look like. This gave me a sense of scale, framing, and color."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img-row","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img","props":{"src":"/images/games/out-of-thyme/20230808230137.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"On to the implementation. I quickly dropped my sketches in and got the player moving around before adding train car collisions. After implementing the scrolling ground, it finally felt like the game was coming together."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img-row","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img","props":{"src":"/images/games/out-of-thyme/20230807082250.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Day 2 was a blur of coding, animating, and debugging. Despite it's punishing difficulty and unpolished sprites, the game was playable!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Day 3 was all about polish: adding outlines to sprites, making the sky change color, adding sound effects, adding instructions, high scores, etc."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I submitted my entry 1 minute and 48 seconds before the deadline. I worked ~40 hours in 3 days and drank lots of coffee. After hitting \"submit,\" there was a "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"huge"}]},{"type":"text","value":" feeling of accomplishment that overcame me. I got to relax, play other submissions, and debrief with my friends about our experience. It wasn't long before we starting talking about the next game jam...once we had all mentally & physically recovered, that is."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img-row","props":{"collapse":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img","props":{"src":"/images/games/out-of-thyme/20230808225229.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img","props":{"src":"/images/games/out-of-thyme/game-gif.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"the-results"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Results"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I feel proud of what I accomplished. Even though it is a small arcade game, I was able to polish it more than previous entries. The game mechanics made sense, were easy to learn, and hard to master. I included hints to help out new players and easily-readable animations when something important happens. The UI was tabbable so you don't need to touch a mouse and break your rhythm. The win screen is animated and interesting...but so is the lose screen (which players might see more often!)."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img-row","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"content-img","props":{"src":"/images/games/out-of-thyme/lose.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Even though these seem like obvious additions in retrospect, it's difficult to prioritize the \"smaller\" items that make a game feel intuitive when under a time crunch. I am happy with what I was able to accomplish...and the 2st place ranking was nice too!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Feel free to play the game for yourself and let me know what you think!"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"the-links","depth":3,"text":"The Links"},{"id":"the-tools","depth":3,"text":"The Tools"},{"id":"the-process","depth":3,"text":"The Process"},{"id":"the-results","depth":3,"text":"The Results"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:projects:games:out-of-thyme.md","_source":"content","_file":"projects/games/out-of-thyme.md","_stem":"projects/games/out-of-thyme","_extension":"md"}